, {"type": "text", "text": ": Captures complex relationships, improves model accuracy, gives deeper data understanding.\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Feature creation"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is part of broader "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "feature engineering"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (creation, transformation, extraction, selection).\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Best practices"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Use domain knowledge, start simple, avoid over-engineering, evaluate impact with cross-validation, iterate, check for redundancy.\n- Feature engineering is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "iterative"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": evaluate → refine → repeat to achieve optimal results."}]}]}}